---
layout: base.njk
title: Home | The Arcades' Studio
---

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="gradient-text mb-8">
      It Came From the Arcades
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-xl shadow-soft dark:shadow-dark-soft inline-block max-w-2xl dark:text-gray-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-arcades-blue dark:hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300">
      A blog about all the stuff I make.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-arcades-pink/10 to-pink-100 dark:from-pink-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/10 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-medium dark:shadow-dark-medium hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-arcades-pink dark:hover:border-pink-500 group">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-arcades-pink rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white mr-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-arcades-pink dark:text-pink-300">Latest Projects</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">Check out my most recent work and ongoing projects. From quirky web apps to surprisingly useful digital experiments!</p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-arcades-green/10 to-green-100 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-green-900/10 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-medium dark:shadow-dark-medium hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-arcades-green dark:hover:border-green-500 group">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-arcades-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white mr-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-arcades-green dark:text-green-300">Blog</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">Read my thoughts, tutorials, and updates on various topics. Warning: may contain unexpected humor and occasional dad jokes!</p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary">Read Blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-arcades-purple/10 to-purple-100 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-purple-900/10 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-medium dark:shadow-dark-medium border-2 border-transparent hover:border-arcades-purple dark:hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-8 text-arcades-purple dark:text-purple-300 text-center">About Me</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-soft dark:shadow-dark-soft border-2 border-transparent hover:border-arcades-purple dark:hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <img src="/img/avatar/austen.jpeg" alt="Austen Tucker" width="100%" height="auto" class="rounded-lg group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg mb-4">
          My name is Austen Tucker, and I make lots of things. Including this blog!
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">
          When I'm not coding, you can find me writing books, making music, and sharing my expertise in project management.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Email Subscription Section -->
  <div id="subscription-form" class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-arcades-blue/10 to-blue-100 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-blue-900/10 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-medium dark:shadow-dark-medium border-2 border-transparent hover:border-arcades-blue dark:hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-arcades-blue dark:text-blue-300">Stay in the Loop!</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg mb-4">
          Subscribe to my newsletter and never miss a new post or project update. I promise only occasional emails with actual useful content (and maybe a pun or two).
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-1 rounded-lg shadow-soft dark:shadow-dark-soft inline-block animate-float">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img src="/img/avatar/maxarcade.jpeg" alt="Max Arcade" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
        <a href="http://eepurl.com/i_PT76" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary text-xl py-4 px-8 inline-flex items-center group">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-3 group-hover:animate-pulse" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M6.503 20.752c0 1.794-1.456 3.248-3.251 3.248-1.796 0-3.252-1.454-3.252-3.248 0-1.794 1.456-3.248 3.252-3.248 1.795.001 3.251 1.454 3.251 3.248zm-6.503-12.572v4.811c6.05.062 10.96 4.966 11.022 11.009h4.817c-.062-8.71-7.118-15.758-15.839-15.82zm0-3.368c10.58.046 19.152 8.594 19.183 19.188h4.817c-.03-13.231-10.755-23.954-24-24v4.812z"/>
          </svg>
          Subscribe to Newsletter
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="mt-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-8 gradient-text inline-block">Latest Posts</h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {%- for post in collections.post | reverse | limit(3) -%}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="card hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300 flex flex-col h-full group">
          {% if post.data.image %}
            <div class="h-48 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          
          <div class="p-6 flex-grow flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-3 text-arcades-blue dark:text-blue-300 group-hover:text-arcades-purple dark:group-hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">
              {{ post.data.title }}
            </h3>
            
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}" class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm dark:text-gray-300 inline-block mb-3">
              {{ post.date | dateReadable }}
            </time>
            
            {% if post.data.description %}
              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 flex-grow">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            
            <span class="text-arcades-purple dark:text-purple-300 font-medium inline-flex items-center group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
              Read more
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      {%- endfor -%}
      
      {% if collections.post.length === 0 %}
        <div class="col-span-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-medium dark:shadow-dark-medium text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-display text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">No posts yet. Check back soon!</p>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    
    {% if collections.post.length > 0 %}
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Posts</a>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div> 